/ COPY + PASTING ENVELOPE POINTS: SAME TRACK

/ ENTER = COPY POINTS IN ACTIVE ENVELOPES ON SELECTED TRACK TO CURSOR - ENVELOPES MUST BE ACTIVE! DE SELECT to PREVENT COPY/PASTE
 
                                     Enter      Reaper  _RSa5270cb7c5e28b002fe880b9108a70434c4915e6                                                            // Envelopes: paste envelope points in time selection in selected envelope at edit cursor
 
/ ENTER = NO  envelope tracks selected: ALL ACTIVE envelopes copied to cursor = FROM time selection leaving position before and after insert as they were.
/ ENTER = ONE Envelope track  selected: ONE ACTIVE envelope  copied to cursor = FROM time selection leaving position before and after insert as they were. 
          
     
         
/ COPY + PASTING ENVELOPE POINTS: OTHER SELECTED TRACKS

/ALT+ENTER = COPY+PASTE ENVELOPE POINTS TO MOUSE POINTER - ENVELOPES DONT NEED TO BE ACTIVE - COPYS A SINGLE SELECTED ENVELOPE SET OF POINTS IN TIME SELECTION, PASTE AT EDIT CURSOR TO ENVELOPE UNDER MOUSE

                                  Alt+Enter      Reaper  _BR_COPY_ENV_TS_SEL_TR_ENVS_MOUSE_CUR      															// Envelopes: paste envelope points in time selection in selected envelope at edit cursor to envelope under mouse pointer 
          	


   
                              Control+Enter      Reaper  _RS82677e647421b6e42f5e810c922d13be0b326938													    	// Script: X-Raym_Copy visible armed envelope of last touched track and paste to selected tracks.lua
                              Control+Enter      Reaper _XENAKIOS_SELFIRSTOFSELTRAX																				// Xenakios/SWS: Select first of selected tracks
                              Control+Enter      Reaper 40296																									// Track: Select all tracks
                              Control+Enter      Reaper _RS82677e647421b6e42f5e810c922d13be0b326938																// Script: X-Raym_Copy visible armed envelope of last touched track and paste to selected tracks.lua
 
     
/ CONTROL+ENTER = COPIES MULTIPLE ENVELOPES TO THE FIRST SELECTED TRACKS FROM THE LAST SELECTED TRACK.(in order track of selection NOT position) WHOLE SONG FROM START TO END OR FIRST SELECTED TRACK TIME SELECTION TO TIME SELCTION TO OTHER SELECTED TRACKS TIME SELECTION- CURSOR HAS NO EFFECT.
/ CONTROL+ENTER = ENVELOPES NEED TO BE ARMED AND VISIBLE ON ALL OF THE SELECTED TRACKS TO COPY. UNARM ENVELOPE ON EITHER THE TRACK YOURE PASTING FROM OR TO, TO PREVENT COPY.



